00:38:44,120 --> 00:38:46,840
I decide if it's worth it.

591
00:38:54,880 --> 00:38:55,470
Mr. Ming.

592
00:38:55,550 --> 00:38:56,120
Mr. Ming.

593
00:38:59,600 --> 00:39:00,400
At the command of His Majesty,

594
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:02,470
we must kill the rosefinch.

595
00:39:03,400 --> 00:39:03,680
But...

596
00:39:04,080 --> 00:39:04,440
But...

597
00:39:05,120 --> 00:39:05,510
Umm...

598
00:39:05,880 --> 00:39:07,270
What are you waiting for?
Encircle this tower!

599
00:39:07,270 --> 00:39:08,360
- Yes.
- Yes.

600
00:39:27,080 --> 00:39:27,680
Yan,

601
00:39:30,270 --> 00:39:31,510
you took revenge.

602
00:39:33,440 --> 00:39:34,950
Why must you hurt common people?

603
00:39:37,160 --> 00:39:38,840
I beg you for one tear.

604
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:41,680
Official Cai told me

605
00:39:42,270 --> 00:39:43,470
the rosefinch flame isn't ordinary

606
00:39:43,470 --> 00:39:44,550
and can't be extinguished.

607
00:39:45,640 --> 00:39:48,880
Only a cold rosefinch's tear

608
00:39:49,510 --> 00:39:50,470
can save this city.

609
00:39:52,550 --> 00:39:53,680
I told you.

610
00:39:54,160 --> 00:39:56,920
I don't smile or cry.

611
00:39:59,990 --> 00:40:00,920
Besides,

612
00:40:02,790 --> 00:40:04,510
they deserve to die.

613
00:40:06,550 --> 00:40:07,160
Yan,

614
00:40:09,270 --> 00:40:11,310
don't you remember what I just said?

615
00:40:14,510 --> 00:40:16,120
When you saw I was dying,

616
00:40:18,160 --> 00:40:19,510
you shed a tear.

617
00:40:22,920 --> 00:40:23,550
Yan.

618
00:40:27,470 --> 00:40:28,680
We have a future.

619
00:40:32,400 --> 00:40:33,080
Mr. Lu,

620
00:40:35,680 --> 00:40:36,790
I've taken revenge.

621
00:40:38,510 --> 00:40:40,080
All I want is to die now.

622
00:40:54,030 --> 00:40:54,840
I just hope.

623
00:40:57,310 --> 00:40:58,440
In the next life,

624
00:41:01,160 --> 00:41:02,160
I could still meet you.

625
00:41:03,120 --> 00:41:04,680
Why can't we be together in this life?

626
00:41:07,400 --> 00:41:08,920
Why can't we?

627
00:41:11,440 --> 00:41:12,080
Yan,

628
00:41:13,680 --> 00:41:14,790
I will pay

629
00:41:16,920 --> 00:41:17,920
for what humans owed you.

630
00:41:19,360 --> 00:41:19,990
What do you say?

631
00:41:27,440 --> 00:41:28,840
You damaged the Tower.

632
00:41:29,160 --> 00:41:30,360
Do you plead guilty?

633
00:42:04,310 --> 00:42:05,230
How could there be

634
00:42:06,120 --> 00:42:07,470
such a powerful demon?

635
00:42:11,790 --> 00:42:12,710
I plead guilty.

636
00:42:13,310 --> 00:42:14,550
Thank you, Miss.

637
00:42:20,550 --> 00:42:21,440
For what?

638
00:42:25,470 --> 00:42:26,200
Mr. Lu,

639
00:42:28,960 --> 00:42:31,480
I thought no one else

640
00:42:32,590 --> 00:42:34,350
would really love me.

641
00:42:36,510 --> 00:42:39,720
I didn't expect to meet you, either.

642
00:42:40,350 --> 00:42:41,350
Yan, I told you.

643
00:42:45,550 --> 00:42:46,680
I'll always be with you.

644
00:42:48,240 --> 00:42:48,750
Don't.

645
00:42:50,030 --> 00:42:51,510
Don't do anything silly, will you?

646
00:42:52,200 --> 00:42:54,030
I've covered all the sins.

647
00:42:55,200 --> 00:42:56,720
There can be no forgiveness.

648
00:42:57,200 --> 00:42:58,240
I totally understand.

649
00:42:59,350 --> 00:43:00,550
I don't care.

650
00:43:02,720 --> 00:43:03,510
The two of us

651
00:43:05,270 --> 00:43:06,590
are destined to go different ways.

652
00:43:09,590 --> 00:43:10,350
Even so,

653
00:43:12,590 --> 00:43:13,920
we can end up together.

654
00:43:26,310 --> 00:43:26,960
Mr. Lu,

655
00:43:30,120 --> 00:43:31,350
I'll see you in the next life.

656
00:43:41,240 --> 00:43:41,680
Look.

657
00:43:42,640 --> 00:43:42,990
What?

658
00:43:42,990 --> 00:43:43,510
Look. Look.

659
00:43:43,920 --> 00:43:44,720
What's that?

660
00:44:22,220 --> 00:44:27,950
♪Here's a flower for you♪

661
00:44:28,610 --> 00:44:33,090
♪I don't know what to say
when we look at each other♪

662
00:44:34,940 --> 00:44:40,730
♪Time goes by so quickly♪

663
00:44:41,080 --> 00:44:46,400
♪My obsession leads to my fate♪

664
00:44:46,900 --> 00:44:52,730
♪Destiny is confusing over the years♪

665
00:44:53,320 --> 00:44:59,270
♪It feels bleak even with the light on♪

666
00:44:59,610 --> 00:45:02,810
♪I see the shadow
when I almost forget you♪

667
00:45:02,810 --> 00:45:06,170
♪A ray of light on my journey♪

668
00:45:06,170 --> 00:45:12,350
♪It's like you're here
to pour out your heart♪

669
00:45:12,470 --> 00:45:18,500
♪Although the memories of our love
bring us pain♪

670
00:45:18,910 --> 00:45:25,060
♪All I ask for is to hold your hand
until the end of time♪

671
00:45:25,220 --> 00:45:28,380
♪Selflessly♪

672
00:45:28,530 --> 00:45:31,940
♪We taste the sorrows and joys♪

673
00:45:32,410 --> 00:45:39,410
♪I'll never let you go
till death do us part♪
